metadata.name: BlackStone town_talisman
metadata.description:
The Series of Gongga is an experiment of creating spaces on crypto that vanishes in the real world. My neighborhood will disappear soon due to redevelopment. Each door of the houses that have already been vacant has the sticker "Vacant House." I plan to restructure the neighborhood in the crypto world.  
The image of the photo is regenerated by a talisman as the colors of the sticker "Vacant House" and the talisman are similar. It narrates that the vacant houses send peace to the real world.
